name: Moment of Life - #Halloween
description:
The first artwork is a series of a girl who enjoys every moment in her life. Feeling the surroundings and the aura of living things.

This frame of “Moment of Life” captures the girl enjoying the festive season of Halloween. She’s very delighted to visit her neighborhood, flying around sharing some treats. Since this is the first time, she’s roaming around the village after “isolated” years of her life.

From here, her journey begins.
